{
  "stem": "33.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 207,
      "text": "But that heaven only lasted sometime in January.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 208,
      "text": "I got there early December.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 209,
      "text": "They needed everybody in the factories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 210,
      "text": "So I worked in the factory with the rest of the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 211,
      "text": "I have to tell you about a good German at this point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 212,
      "text": "There was this 24 year old, very simple, semi-educated SS woman who was in charge of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 213,
      "text": "We had a little girl-- her name was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 214,
      "text": "She was from Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 215,
      "text": "An 18 year old-- my age-- who worked also in the potato peeling room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 216,
      "text": "And she was an epileptic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 217,
      "text": "I never know how she made it and how they-- she probably just left the camp before they were discovered.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 218,
      "text": "She looked good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 219,
      "text": "She did have these seizures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 220,
      "text": "I've never seen anything like these before or after, but it is not a pretty sight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 221,
      "text": "Whenever she had a seizure, we sent for Anne-Lise, this SS woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 222,
      "text": "She came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 223,
      "text": "She would, basically, pick her up, and kiss her, and, and comfort her, and you know, be there for her until the seizure was over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 224,
      "text": "And she was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 225,
      "text": "She was an SS woman, but she was just a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 226,
      "text": "She was never exposed to a death camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 227,
      "text": "She did not know what's going on, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 228,
      "text": "She wasn't-- she joined the SS-- I don't know, probably that was the only job she could get.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 229,
      "text": "And she was one of the few good Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 230,
      "text": "In the-- the person who told me not to tell people was-- if he caught women trying to steal potato peels or discarded rotten vegetables from the garbage bins, he would beat them up fiercely.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 231,
      "text": "I mean he was not one of the nice guys, definitely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 232,
      "text": "But he wasn't-- he was in charge of the camp, because he lived there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
